{"article_id":"HjHjxgl5vYJ3Aldj","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"'They 're Talking To People ' :","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"Tensions Ease In Ferguson","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"As Police Change Tactics","depth":2},{"id":3,"text":"St. Louis Police Chief Sam Dotson taking a selfie with a protestor .","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"This is a CHANGED atmosphere .","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"# Ferguson","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"pic.","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"twitter.com/Jm51iZXdvz","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"- Yamiche Alcindor","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"( @ Yamiche )","depth":5},{"id":10,"text":"August 15 , 2014","depth":4},{"id":11,"text":"Ferguson , Mo. , saw more protests last night","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"-","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"but","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"instead of meeting demonstrators with tear gas and armored vehicles ,","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"police walked with them ,","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"and posed for photos .","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"The shift came after days of clashes","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"sparked by the police killing of unarmed black teenager Michael Brown .","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"`` There was no line of armored trucks or police in riot gear","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"blocking traffic Thursday night .","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"The few police officers","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"spotted in the crowd","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"were wearing regular uniforms . ``","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"Gov . Jay Nixon placed Missouri State Highway Patrol Capt . Ron Johnson in charge on Thursday afternoon , instead of the St. Louis County police .","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"The result was an atmosphere","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"that felt more like a party . ``","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"Protester Dante Kelly hoped","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"the night was a tipping point .","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"`` 'But it 's only a start , '","depth":13},{"id":30,"text":"he said .","depth":13},{"id":31,"text":"'Captain Johnson is not going to be here forever ,","depth":14},{"id":32,"text":"so , ai n't no telling . ' `` Other protesters shared Kelly 's skepticism","depth":14},{"id":33,"text":"that the change would be permanent .","depth":13},{"id":34,"text":"And many expressed their frustration","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"that the police had not yet released the name of the shooter . ''","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"The Missouri Highway Patrol ,","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"which has taken over security in Ferguson ,","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"says","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"that no arrests of demonstrators were made Thursday ,","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"confirming reports of a peaceful protest .","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"Capt . Ron Johnson said","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"people , and the police , need to continue that trend .","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"`` In our anger , we have to make sure","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"we do n't burn down our own house , ''","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"Johnson said .","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"He also said","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"he welcomed the use of cameras","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"to record police work ,","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"saying","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"that they `` do n't change our jobs . ''","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"Johnson also acknowledged criticism of the way","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"in which Ferguson Police Chief Thomas Jackson released the name of Darren Wilson , the officer","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"who shot and killed Brown , 18 .","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"The chief did not take questions ,","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"and he added new information about last Saturday ,","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"including the news","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"that Brown was suspected of stealing cigars from a convenience store","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"about 10 minutes before he was stopped .","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"The investigation into Brown 's death is continuing , and on several fronts .","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"Soon after the shooting , Jackson asked the St. Louis County police to handle the inquiry ;","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"the FBI and Justice Department are also conducting their own investigation .","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"But the key difference in Ferguson on Thursday was that police had changed their approach","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"to trying to prevent a repeat of the violence and property damage","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"that occurred Sunday .","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"Police were heavily criticized for using tear gas ,","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"deploying heavy weapons","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"and arresting journalists .","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"`` They made it look like they were over in Iraq ,","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"ready to attack us , ''","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"protester Marquess Mull tells NPR 's Cheryl Corley .","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"But Thursday was different ,","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"he said :","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"`` They 're talking to people . ''","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"'They 're Talking To People ' :","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"Tensions Ease In Ferguson","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"As Police Change Tactics","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"Listen · 2:15","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"2:15","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"The new commander , Johnson , is a Ferguson native","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"who is also black .","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"He and Jackson had both said","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"police would change both their tactics and their appearance in an effort","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"to avoid provoking protesters .","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"The military-style gear and the gas masks would be stowed ,","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"they said .","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"`` When we talk about boots on the ground , ''","depth":14},{"id":87,"text":"Johnson said at a news conference Thursday ,","depth":14},{"id":88,"text":"`` my boots are going to be on the ground .","depth":13},{"id":89,"text":"And so we are going to have a different approach","depth":13},{"id":90,"text":"and have the approach","depth":14},{"id":91,"text":"that we are in this together . ''","depth":14},{"id":92,"text":"Johnson kept that promise last night ,","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"walking with demonstrators ,","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"hugging people ,","depth":13},{"id":95,"text":"and representing authority in a way","depth":13},{"id":96,"text":"that 's been absent this week .","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"The community responded with a spirited demonstration","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"that was marked by cheers and the honking horns of passing cars .","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"One woman told Johnson ,","depth":12},{"id":100,"text":"`` Thank you so much for coming out here tonight , ''","depth":12},{"id":101,"text":"according to The Washington Post 's Wesley Lowery .","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"`` Thank you so much for coming out here tonight , ''","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"woman says to Johnson , almost in tears","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"pic.twitter.com/Q6kS96bCM","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"4 - Wesley Lowery","depth":8},{"id":106,"text":"( @ WesleyLowery )","depth":8},{"id":107,"text":"August 14 , 2014","depth":7},{"id":108,"text":"This week , scenes of grief and confrontation in Ferguson have further stoked racial tensions in the town","depth":6},{"id":109,"text":"that 's two-thirds black ,","depth":6},{"id":110,"text":"and the images and stories have resonated far beyond the town .","depth":5},{"id":111,"text":"In a show of solidarity , thousands of protesters in New York , Washington and other cities held their own demonstrations last night ,","depth":6},{"id":112,"text":"chanting the phrase","depth":8},{"id":113,"text":"that has rung through Ferguson 's streets this week :","depth":8},{"id":114,"text":"`` Hands up , do n't shoot , ''","depth":8},{"id":115,"text":"a reference to witnesses ' claims","depth":9},{"id":116,"text":"that Brown had his hands up","depth":10},{"id":117,"text":"when he was fatally shot Saturday .","depth":10},{"id":118,"text":"In Ferguson , the new tone was indicated most simply , and perhaps most adorably , by a Thomas the Train parade vehicle","depth":7},{"id":119,"text":"that plied the same streets","depth":8},{"id":120,"text":"where armored vehicles had recently roamed .","depth":8},{"id":121,"text":"It carried a group of smiling young men .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":243,"left":124,"right":242,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":124,"left":123,"right":2,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":123,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":242,"left":131,"right":241,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":131,"left":128,"right":130,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":128,"left":126,"right":127,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":126,"left":125,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":125,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":127,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":130,"left":129,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":129,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":241,"left":227,"right":240,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":227,"left":181,"right":226,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":181,"left":160,"right":180,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":160,"left":138,"right":159,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":138,"left":136,"right":137,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":136,"left":132,"right":135,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":132,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":135,"left":13,"right":134,"re